/*===========================================================================
  merge_frey_osborne_prob.do

Objective: To map the computerization possibilities of the OCCSOC variable in IPUMS USA to Frey & Osborne (2017).

Corrections:
		1. Observations with occsoc == 0 are deleted before merge.
		2. Condition `prob_computer != .` added to risk_category definition.
(In Stata, missing (.) is considered greater than any number, so the >= 0.70 condition was also putting missings at high risk)
		3. Tempfile is created before the main data is opened (previous error fixed)
		4. Average probability added for IPUMS aggregate SOC codes (121 codes)
Method: For codes ending in 0, the average of sub-codes sharing the same prefix was taken. Military professions (55xxxx) were left missing.
===========================================================================*/

