* 1. SETTINGS — edit only these two lines.
* -----------------------------------------------------------------------
local ipums_file  "ipumslabor.dta"
local output_file "ipumslabor_matched.dta"

* -----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 2. CREATE CROSSWALK AND SAVE IT TO TEMPFILE
* -----------------------------------------------------------------------
tempfile crosswalk
clear

input str6 occsoc_raw double prob_computer
